title: Exploratory Visualization
description: Designed and implemented a static visualization project focusing on effective data communication. Created a targeted visualization answering a specific research question, incorporating appropriate visual encodings, transformations, and design elements to tell a compelling data story while maintaining clarity and interpretability.

title: Food Recipe Rating Predictor
description: Developed a machine learning model to predict recipe ratings based on ingredients, cooking time, and complexity. The system analyzes recipe components and characteristics to forecast potential user ratings, helping home cooks and food bloggers optimize their recipes.
